#Approach:

Set Matrix Zeroes – Optimal In-Place Approach

Is problem me hume agar kisi cell me 0 mile,
to uski poori row aur poori column ko 0 karna hota hai.
Challenge ye hai ki ye kaam in-place karna hai, extra matrix use nahi karni.

Isliye hum 0th row aur 0th column ko marker ki tarah use karte hain.

Sabse pehle separately check karte hain ki 0th row me koi 0 hai ya nahi
aur 0th column me koi 0 hai ya nahi.
Iske liye do boolean variables rakhte hain: rowZero aur colZero.

Ab matrix ke remaining part ko traverse karte hain (1,1 se start karke).
Jahan bhi 0 mile, us row ka marker matrix[i][0] ko 0 kar do
aur us column ka marker matrix[0][j] ko 0 kar do.

Ab 0th row ko dekh kar un columns ko zero karo jinke markers 0 hain.
Phir 0th column ko dekh kar un rows ko zero karo jinke markers 0 hain.

End me agar initially 0th row me zero tha to poori 0th row ko 0 kar do,
aur agar initially 0th column me zero tha to poori 0th column ko 0 kar do.

Is tarah hum extra space use kiye bina matrix ko modify kar dete hain.

Time Complexity: O(n * m)
Space Complexity: O(1)

#Code:
class Solution {
    public void setZeroes(int[][] matrix) {
        boolean rowZero = false;
        boolean colZero = false;
        int n = matrix.length;
        int m = matrix[0].length;

        //finding zero in row zero
        for(int j=0; j<m; j++){
            if(matrix[0][j] == 0){
                rowZero = true;
            }
        }

        //finding zero in column zero
        for(int i=0; i<n; i++){
            if(matrix[i][0] == 0){
                colZero = true;
            }
        }

        //Traversing in small matrix
        for(int i=1; i<n; i++){
            for(int j=1; j<m; j++){
                if(matrix[i][j] == 0){
                    matrix[0][j] = 0;
                    matrix[i][0] = 0;
                }
            }
        }

        //traversing in 0th row
        for(int j=1; j<m; j++){
            if(matrix[0][j] == 0){
                for(int i=1; i<n; i++){
                    matrix[i][j] = 0;
                }
            }
        }

        //traversing in 0th column
        for(int i=1; i<n; i++){
            if(matrix[i][0] == 0){
                for(int j=1; j<m; j++){
                    matrix[i][j] = 0;
                }
            }
        }

        //Check if zero row contains any 0
        if(rowZero == true){
            for(int j=0; j<m; j++){
                matrix[0][j] = 0;
            }
        }

        //Check if zero column contains any 0
        if(colZero == true){
            for(int i=0; i<n; i++){
                matrix[i][0] = 0;
            }
        }
    }
}
